Definition: the right of the state to take private property for public use
Example: the Fifth Amendment that was added to the Constitution of the United States requires that just compensation be made
Synonyms: legal_right, noun, group, law, c, the, right, of, state, to, take, private, property, for, public, use, Fifth, Amendment, that, was, added, Constitution, United, States, requires, just, compensation, be, made
Category: noun.attribute
